&lt;ul class=&quot;[&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc space-y-2.5 pl-7&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Own the strategic roadmap, investment decisions, and revenue accountability for our Accenture partnership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Build and maintain executive relationships within Accenture&#39;s leadership to position Claude as the foundational technology for their AI practice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Develop comprehensive enablement programs that help Accenture&#39;s global workforce understand Claude&#39;s capabilities and differentiation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Partner with Accenture to co-develop industry-specific solutions and reference architectures that showcase Claude&#39;s unique capabilities in reasoning, safety, and enterprise readiness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Establish success criteria for joint accounts and create feedback loops that drive continuous improvement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Lead the pursuit of significant enterprise deals through our partnership, ensuring proper positioning and support throughout complex sales cycles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
