&lt;p&gt;This is a high-impact role requiring someone who can operate at the executive level with Deloitte&#39;s global leadership while simultaneously driving tactical wins across priority markets. You will own the strategic roadmap, investment decisions, and revenue accountability for what will become one of Anthropic&#39;s most important partnerships.&lt;/p&gt;
