&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Develop and execute joint go-to-market strategies that drive partner-sourced and partner-influenced pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Lead partner business planning, including setting mutual goals, identifying target accounts, and defining success metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Work directly with partner sales teams to identify opportunities, support deal progression, and close business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
