&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;7+ years of experience in partner sales, channel sales, or partner management at a technology company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Demonstrated success driving revenue through partner channels, with a track record of meeting or exceeding sales targets&lt;/li&gt;
