&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Experience with CRM systems and partner relationship management tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Comfort with ambiguity and the ability to create structure in emerging programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Willingness to travel globally to support partner relationships and joint customer engagements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
